Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Comment: 10,0:01:23.48,0:01:24.23,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hm?
Comment: 0,0:01:30.45,0:01:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:00.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.05,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Friede!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.22,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Hey! It’s been a while!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.35,0:03:23.06,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Looks like you’re doing well, Cap.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.15,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Friede!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.36,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Why the surprise visit?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.82,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I thought you were busy at Exceed.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.87,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Things’ve finally quieted down, \N so I got them to give me a day off.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.87,0:03:43.66,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Dropped in to invite you along \N on some fieldwork.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.04,0:03:46.83,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Wanna come see \N some awesome Pokémon?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.21,0:03:49.17,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.38,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.38,0:03:54.09,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,What’s wrong? \N I thought you’d be ecstatic...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.09,0:03:59.47,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Oh, it’s just that, well... \N We’ve seen plenty of awesome Pokémon already.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.84,0:04:03.31,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,The Rakua adventure \N was mega-awesome, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.31,0:04:05.85,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,So we figured we’d relax for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.27,0:04:10.35,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Sure, relaxation is important too, but...\N I finally got some time off!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.11,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,We oughta do {\i1}something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.82,0:04:16.03,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Well, I {\i1}did{\i0} wanna train with Roy...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.03,0:04:18.57,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,But he says he ain’t got no motivation.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.57,0:04:22.99,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{\q2}Oh, like {\i1}you{\i0} haven’t been going “Tomorrow, tomorrow” \N for who {\i1}knows{\i0} how many days now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.99,0:04:27.00,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Well, me and Yamirami \N are {\i1}already{\i} strongest, anyhow.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.79,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I’ve really got to record \N some new Gurumin vids, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.79,0:04:33.63,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,But... I’m really blanking on ideas.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.13,0:04:36.55,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Sounds like you’ve all \N just been spacing out.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.09,0:04:39.51,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Liko... How about you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.51,0:04:40.59,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.64,0:04:43.14,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.94,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,All right! \N Then let’s set off straight away!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.94,0:04:49.77,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.19,0:04:52.02,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,That okay, Captain?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.14,0:05:25.60,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Muscles of a Saidon...{Zir's screen name, Muscles_of_a_Saidon}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.14,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I wonder how Mr. Zir{Honorifics note: Zir-san}’s doing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.91,0:05:48.08,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,There’s so many Cocoon...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.08,0:05:50.79,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,There could be Spear nearby. \N Be careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.71,0:05:59.55,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,When you were a Hogator, there was \N that whole mess with a Beequeen chasing you...{When you were a Hogator, you got chased by a Beequeen and it was trouble}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.96,0:06:04.84,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,But don’t worry. You could take down \N a whole {\i1}pack{\i0} of Spear now, Loudbone! {"pack" is sort of odd for bugs imo, but there's probably not a great word for both hornets and large flightless birds -ed}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.80,0:06:06.72,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.72,0:06:08.85,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,A pack’s approaching.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.93,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Huh? It couldn’t be...!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.23,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Oh, it was just some Dodo...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.23,0:06:23.53,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,That time I got chased by \N a buncha Dodrio was a real nightmare. {When I got chased by some Dodrios before, it was really rough.}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.66,0:06:32.50,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Hey, Master... You {\i1}sure{\i0} there’s some kinda \N mega-awesome Pokémon ‘round here? {tone: implying he doubts the idea, prodding for more info}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.50,0:06:34.21,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,How far do we have to go?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.21,0:06:37.21,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,We’re nearly there. \N As soon as we get through this...{133}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.21,0:06:43.47,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,The Pokémon I want you \N to investigate is here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.68,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What kind of Pokémon is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.68,0:06:46.22,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.01,0:06:50.10,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’s a Hinbass!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.10,0:06:52.27,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hinbass?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.27,0:06:56.60,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,I’d like for you to catch \N the Hinbass that lives in this lake.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.69,0:07:00.82,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,Hinbass. Fish Pokémon. \N Water type.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.82,0:07:04.24,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,It is ragged and shabby{partial Scarlet/etc dex entry}, \N and is paid no attention by anyone. {partial Ruby dex entry}{re-edited from "and is largely ignored." to be more usable in this episode. -ed}{not-ignore line}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.24,0:07:08.37,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,It has a hardy life force, \N but is slow and easy to catch.{partial Sapphire dex entry}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.37,0:07:10.79,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Ragged and shabby...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.79,0:07:13.00,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Paid no attention by anyone... {not-ignore line}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.00,0:07:15.12,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,What’s mega-awesome about {\i1}that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.12,0:07:18.04,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,When it evolves, \N it becomes Milokallos!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.63,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Milokallos, huh...?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.96,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,We battled one of those \N at the Shining Pond.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.22,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,That brings back memories!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.22,0:07:29.01,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Yeah. We’ve already fought a Milokallos, \N so if it’s a {\i1}Hinbass{\i0} we’re up against...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.22,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Catching it’ll be a snap.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.18,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Oho. You sure about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.02,0:07:36.23,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Well then, just give it a go!
Comment: 10,0:07:53.16,0:07:56.25,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Khhhhhh...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.25,0:07:59.17,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Argh! I’m not hookin’ {\i1}anything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.67,0:08:02.67,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Is it really even here?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.93,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Yo, Hinbass! Get out here!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.93,0:08:12.10,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Quit it, Ult! \N You’re just gonna spook it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.40,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,There it is! The Hinbass!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.40,0:08:23.15,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’m{\i0} gonna be the one to catch it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.65,0:08:30.07,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Awright! Easy win! {楽勝}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.07,0:08:30.70,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.91,0:08:34.16,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,{\i1}Augh!{\i0} One more time!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.16,0:08:36.08,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Now it’s my turn!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.79,0:08:41.83,Main,Roy Ult,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.55,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,What’s the big idea, Roy?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.55,0:08:46.80,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I could ask you the same thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.47,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Just stay outta my way, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.47,0:08:50.38,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{\i1}You’re{\i0} the one getting in {\i1}my{\i0} way!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.09,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Wha—?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.47,0:08:52.68,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Urk!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.68,0:08:53.30,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I’ve got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.39,0:08:56.81,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I-It’s heavy...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.31,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’ll help you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.31,0:09:00.81,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ready, and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.07,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Yadoran?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.87,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Tough luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.67,0:09:24.34,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,That Hinbass is something else.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.34,0:09:25.50,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.55,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Fishing it up might not be so easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.55,0:09:29.13,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,New plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.22,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wanival. Head underwater \N and corner that Hinbass!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.26,0:09:37.47,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,When it pops out of the water, \N Masquernya...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.10,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,...can hook it on her vine!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.99,0:09:52.74,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.49,0:09:57.91,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Catch Hinbass with your vine!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.96,0:10:02.25,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}We did it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.59,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Aww, so close!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.35,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Grrr... Yamirami! Power Gem!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.94,0:10:24.56,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wanival, catch{kyatchi} it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.36,0:10:31.57,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Loudbone! Flare Song!
Comment: 10,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.49,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.04,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Just what {\i1}is{\i0} that Hinbass?!
Comment: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:54.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Comment: 10,0:11:06.35,0:11:07.81,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.45,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.45,0:11:20.20,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,How come we can’t even \N get a {\i1}foothold...?{\i0} {How come we can't get even one leg up...}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.83,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Seems like you’re having trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.33,0:11:27.08,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,But the Index says \N it’s slow and easy to catch...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.08,0:11:30.75,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,The Index isn’t the final word \N on Pokémon ecology{/biology}.{seitai}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.75,0:11:35.76,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\q2}They’ve each got their own quirks. \N All stuff you’d never know without meeting them in person!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.51,0:11:37.51,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.51,0:11:39.09,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,It’s mega-awesome, that’s for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.56,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Now I’m mega-mega-fired up!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.81,0:11:45.81,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I wanna learn more about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.40,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I’ll catch it! Just you wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.57,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Let’s all work together!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.61,0:11:56.24,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Once it Flops, \N it’ll be in midair and defenseless!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.24,0:11:57.61,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,If we seize that moment...! {TL: If we aim for that moment...!}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.50,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Now, Loudbone!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.33,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Stop it from moving \N with Charm Voice!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.63,0:12:11.50,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Yamirami! Eerie Light!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.51,0:12:17.51,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.51,0:12:17.51,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wanival!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.51,0:12:18.43,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wave Tackle!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.93,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Acrobatics!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.61,0:12:34.02,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait up, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.11,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Let’s go after it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.82,0:12:39.82,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,I’ll be making dinner \N at sundown, y’hear?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.83,0:12:44.66,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It’s not tiring out at all...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.33,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,It’s got mega-stamina!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.34,0:12:56.17,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Almost like it has us in mind...{As in not-ignoring, related to 13:00}{related to the not-ignore lines}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.26,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.34,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Hmph! What a show-off!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.84,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.84,0:13:03.22,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,...it wants {\i1}us{\i0} to \N pay it some attention?{calls back to dex entry, directly inverted like 'to not-ignore it'. Dex: Nobody gives it any company/time of day. Dot: Maybe it wants company/the time of day from us?  Derplit aite o shinai: 'nobody is [ever] the other party to it (in conversation, battle, etc)', which the ENgame fitted to 'is largely ignored'. This Hinbass wants someone to be an the other party to it. Dex entry maybe best changed to 'nobody pays it any attention'}{not-ignore line}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.22,0:13:03.72,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.39,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,That’s why it’s doing this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.44,0:13:11.48,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.98,0:13:13.31,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.02,0:13:18.03,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Shabby or not, its scales’re still {\i1}mega-cool{\i0} \N once you get a good look at ‘em!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.03,0:13:21.07,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Yeah. They’re proof of \N the hardy life it’s lived.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.07,0:13:21.78,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.78,0:13:24.95,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I was never into Hinbass before, \N but now I think they’re great!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.63,0:13:39.76,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Look, it’s the Dodo from before!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.06,0:13:49.52,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Huh?! A Dodo started flying?!{move name, past tense}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.98,0:13:52.52,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It’s like it’s kicking off the air to go even higher! {literally all of these Dodo are male, but there's probably no need to gender the relevant lines. -ed}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.52,0:13:57.02,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Maybe it’s dreamed of getting to Fly? \N Just like Cap did...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.23,0:14:03.57,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,When we saw these Dodo earlier, \N I didn’t realize there was one like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.91,0:14:07.03,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Wait, what? It’s gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.04,0:14:11.41,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.41,0:14:15.71,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It’s gotta have some {\i1}crazy{\i0} muscles \N to Flop across dry land like that...
Comment: 10,0:14:21.84,0:14:22.55,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ahh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.43,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,That’s some finesse...{~~They're dextrous...~~ ~~They're deft handed...~~ ~~They're handy...~~ Ideally would like an EN word that doesn't bring up hands}{went with finesse. hopefully it fits with timeskip-mature-Roy. it's also in somewhat popular slang use now. -ed}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.81,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,They’re using their threads like ropes.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.81,0:14:34.40,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I always pictured \N Cocoon being immobile...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.32,0:14:46.24,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Its guard is down. \N We’ll catch it this time, Wanival!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.04,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.87,0:14:52.83,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}A surfing Saidon?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.54,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,They can {\i1}do{\i0} that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.05,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.68,0:15:09.05,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,...it observed how Water-type Pokémon \N and people move, and copied them!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.85,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Even within the same species, \N they’re all distinct! {alluding to Friede 11:30, but without a direct wording echo}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.85,0:15:14.77,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Innerestin’! \N Let’s go find some more!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.77,0:15:17.73,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Wait, Ult! \N We gotta find Hinbass first!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.73,0:15:20.27,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,I can look for Hinbass along the way!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.78,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,I’m gonna check out \N {\i1}every{\i0} Pokémon livin’ here!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.45,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,He’s so reckless...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.11,0:16:09.41,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.16,0:16:11.70,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,You sure worked hard!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.91,0:16:15.00,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,The Hinbass got away...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.08,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,So frustrating...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.08,0:16:17.87,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,We got {\i1}so{\i0} close a few times, though...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.46,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,It was unreal.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.42,0:16:25.84,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Well, it {\i1}is{\i} the Strongest Hinbass, \N which no one’s ever managed to catch, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.84,0:16:26.55,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.55,0:16:28.34,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Strongest...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.55,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.05,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Didn’t I mention?{catchphrase}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.85,0:16:34.22,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}You did not!{\i0}{076}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.43,0:16:40.35,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Ahh, that hit the spot!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.90,0:16:44.36,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,We didn’t manage to catch Hinbass, \N but we had a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.36,0:16:49.36,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Yeah. Don’t think I’ve gotten that much exercise \N in a {\i1}long{\i0} time. My muscles are already aching.{lit: I already have sore muscles}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.20,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,It really was amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.33,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,We got to meet \N lots of interesting Pokémon.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.33,0:16:57.54,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,And there’s still \N loads of ‘em we {\i1}ain’t{\i0} met!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.96,0:17:02.42,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,The world’s huge! \N Pokémon’re so {\i1}deep!{\i0}{PV (2nd half)}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.96,0:17:04.92,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Adventures never end.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.46,0:17:09.42,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Even if you feel like you’re all burnt out, \N you’ll end up aching for more.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.93,0:17:12.89,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Excitement never stops.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.16,0:17:41.42,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.59,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What’s going on? It’s so early...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.59,0:17:49.67,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Shh! Just watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.03,0:19:01.62,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,You know, \N with the Rakua adventure over...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.70,0:19:05.42,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I wasn’t sure \N what I wanted to do next.{PV}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.67,0:19:08.29,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,But I’ve got it figured out now.{PV}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.29,0:19:12.67,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I want to keep having exciting adventures; \N keep taking on heart-pounding challenges...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.67,0:19:15.51,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,...alongside all of you, just like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.51,0:19:17.47,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,With Masquernya and everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.47,0:19:23.81,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,And Roy, Dot, and Ult... \N I want to keep having adventures...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.81,0:19:25.48,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,...as the Rising Voltteccers!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.48,0:19:27.77,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I feel the same way!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.77,0:19:30.65,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I wanna travel to brand-new places \N with all of you,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.65,0:19:33.24,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,and I wanna sing with Loudbone \N all across the world!{PV (fragment)}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.74,0:19:37.11,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Same here!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.11,0:19:40.49,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I wanna learn so much more about Pokémon! \N Don’t you, Wanival?{PV (first sentence)}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.49,0:19:46.12,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Yeah! There’s loadsa \N strong Pokémon out there, after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.12,0:19:48.79,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,We’re gonna keep aiming \N for {\i1}strongest,{\i0} Yamirami!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.71,0:19:55.76,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Isn’t that just \N the most beautiful sight, Cap?{keshiki}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.01,0:20:04.06,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,We’ve been slacking off for a while, \N but now, once more...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.77,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please journey with us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.89,0:20:10.02,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,We’d been slacking, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.11,Main,Molly,0,0,0,,We’ve gotta muster up some spirit again!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.11,0:20:14.40,Main,Orio,0,0,0,,I’ll go all out, \N and get this ship really {\i1}movin’{\i0} again! {121:really get movin’}{I'll make this ship really fly(fast)[121:really get movin’] again, with everything I've got!}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.99,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,All right! Let’s get this ship \N prepped to set sail!{We'll get straight to the preparations to set sail!}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.99,0:20:18.66,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Everyone... Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.66,0:20:21.53,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Hey! First, how about we do... \N y’know, {\i1}that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.66,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,The hand sign! Good idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.66,0:20:24.91,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Let’s do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.33,0:20:29.83,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,That reminds me... \N Where’s old man Landau?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.83,0:20:31.84,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I haven’t seen him at all lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.84,0:20:35.46,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Oh, Gramps said he had \N other business to attend to.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.88,0:20:39.30,Main,People,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa! It’s Mighty G!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.30,0:20:42.80,Main,Mighty G,0,0,0,,Grk... Surpass your potential!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.80,0:20:49.64,Main,Mighty G,0,0,0,,Your heart is always \N with your friends! Mighty G!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.11,0:20:53.77,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Rising Voltteccers...{PV}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.65,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Reboot!{PV}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.32,Main,Everyone,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah!{\i0}{PV}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.12,0:21:09.16,Main,Orio,0,0,0,,You did a fine job rekindling them.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.16,0:21:10.00,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.00,0:21:13.46,Main,Orio,0,0,0,,You invited them out for fieldwork \N {\i1}knowing{\i0} all this’d happen, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.80,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Oh {\i1}did{\i0} I now...?{'Oh, I wonder. ;)'} See ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.76,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,I’ll be back to visit.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.69,0:21:34.90,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,The Brave Asagi sets sail!
Comment: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:45.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie A}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.29,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Friede here!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.29,0:21:51.87,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’s time to Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.08,0:21:55.46,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Today’s topic is Hinbass!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.46,0:21:58.21,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’s a Pokémon \N with a strong life force,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.21,0:22:01.59,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,but do you know \N what kind of habitat it lives in?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.01,0:22:06.56,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,See the answer after the commercials!
Comment: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:06.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:36.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie B}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.36,0:23:42.53,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Now, time to announce \N the correct answer!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.53,0:23:43.82,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,The answer is...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.82,0:23:45.57,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,All of them!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.07,0:23:50.33,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’ll live anywhere there’s water... \N {\i1}That’s{\i0} how tough a Pokémon it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.70,0:23:53.33,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,That sure was one incredible Hinbass.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.04,0:23:57.33,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I wonder what it’s up to now.
Comment: 0,0:24:00.59,0:24:00.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.21,0:24:04.21,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,The Brave Asagi sets sail!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.13,0:24:07.51,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Another adventure \N with everyone begins!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.51,0:24:09.64,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,We’re finally on the move!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.64,0:24:10.97,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,What’s all this...?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.97,0:24:14.68,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,The Rising Voltteccers’ exploits \N have made the news!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.68,0:24:16.48,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh? When we’ve only just set off?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.48,0:24:17.27,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.27,0:24:19.35,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I don’t have a clue either...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.35,0:24:20.86,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Let’s go and investigate.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.86,0:24:24.53,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,And so, to be continued \N next time on Pocket Monsters...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.53,0:24:26.82,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,The Fake Rising Voltteccers Appear?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.82,0:24:30.53,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Fakes, huh? \N If yer fixin’ to battle, I’ll take you on!{Intentional scenebleed for the start}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
