Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:21.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur5\pos(960,22)\bord9\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Gonna give my motivation button a little tap!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:22.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur5\pos(960,22)\bord9\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}The power of hard work is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:23.32,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur5\pos(960,22)\bord9\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Ahem!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:24.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur5\pos(960,22)\bord9\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}But if I slack off I might end up devolving...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:25.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur5\pos(960,22)\bord9\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Well, that’s no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:26.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur5\pos(960,22)\bord9\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}But now you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:30.04,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur5\pos(960,22)\bord9\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}I know button mashing won’t help at all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:32.54,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur5\pos(960,22)\bord9\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}So stop shaking this maiden’s heart already
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:33.29,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur5\pos(960,22)\bord9\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Stop it!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:36.29,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur5\pos(960,22)\bord9\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Getting attached, but then they turn away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:39.55,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur5\pos(960,22)\bord9\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}When things just don’t go the way that you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.55,0:22:42.92,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur5\pos(960,22)\bord9\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Isn’t it so fun? Doesn’t it make your heart race?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.05,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur5\pos(960,22)\bord9\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Doesn’t it make you all excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:47.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur5\pos(960,22)\bord9\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}When I feel a spark...
